{"CLs":[{"__type":"IST","EID":"b5b66102-4c45-467e-8a7f-99f59e836cef","H":513.99999999999977,"TXT":"\/\/ Initialize value\u000d\u000aHMI_Press_Ton.Total_Tonnage := 0;\u000d\u000aTonnage_Total_C := 0;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a\/\/ Determine the total number of strain links\u000d\u000aIF (HMI_Press_Ton_Ret.Strain_L_Four) THEN\u000d\u000a\u0009X_Max := 3;\u000d\u000aELSE\u000d\u000a\u0009X_Max := 1;\u000d\u000aEND_IF;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a\/\/ Add up all the strain links to equal total tonnage\u000d\u000aFOR X := 0 TO X_Max DO\u000d\u000a\u0009HMI_Press_Ton.Total_Tonnage := HMI_Press_Ton.Total_Tonnage + HMI_Press_Ton.Tonnage[X];\u000d\u000a\u0009Tonnage_Total_C := Tonnage_Total_C + Strain_L[X].Tonnage_C;\u000d\u000aEND_FOR;\u000d\u000a\u000d\u000a\/\/ On rising edge of tonnage above the limit trigger the alarm\u000d\u000aTonnage_Above_SP_R(CLK := (HMI_Press_Ton.Total_Tonnage > HMI_Press_Ton_Ret.Press_Tonnage_Alarm_SP));\u000d\u000aIF (Tonnage_Above_SP_R.Q AND HMI_Press_Ton_Ret.M_StrainL) THEN\u000d\u000a\u0009Press_IOL_Tonnage_Alarm := TRUE;\u000d\u000aEND_IF;","W":864}],"CMT":"Provide total tonnage and trigger alarm if necessary.","LRI":1,"RRI":2,"VLs":[]}
